{"tid":530131,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"HKT48 Non-球迷討論區十八回:美久黨需要你","createTime":"2018-01-15T13:04:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-31T13:22:07.000Z","uid":46688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"db5f260f2d4dcc75d2a6730d984627099c9afa19","tid":530131,"uid":46688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T13:04:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://holland.pk/158thy70\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F158thy70&h=5975e04a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">HKT48，由作詞家秋元康擔任總製作人、以福岡市為主要活動據點的女子偶像團體，成立於2011年，團名源自福岡的地名博多（HAKATA）</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">成員名單</span></span><br />\nTeam H<br />\n<img src=\"http://stage48.net/wiki/images/thumb/c/cf/TeamHNovember2017.png/454px-TeamHNovember2017.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstage48.net%2Fwiki%2Fimages%2Fthumb%2Fc%2Fcf%2FTeamHNovember2017.png%2F454px-TeamHNovember2017.png&h=9a793497&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTeam KIV<br />\n<img src=\"http://stage48.net/wiki/images/thumb/f/fc/TeamKIVNovember2017.png/500px-TeamKIVNovember2017.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstage48.net%2Fwiki%2Fimages%2Fthumb%2Ff%2Ffc%2FTeamKIVNovember2017.png%2F500px-TeamKIVNovember2017.png&h=248fd5c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTeam TII<br />\n<img src=\"http://stage48.net/wiki/images/thumb/a/ab/TeamTIINovember2017.png/472px-TeamTIINovember2017.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstage48.net%2Fwiki%2Fimages%2Fthumb%2Fa%2Fab%2FTeamTIINovember2017.png%2F472px-TeamTIINovember2017.png&h=a34918ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n四期生去向<br />\n運上弘菜 KⅣ<br />\n小田彩加 TII<br />\n堺萌香 TII<br />\n清水梨央 TII<br />\n武田智加 TII<br />\n地頭江音々 KⅣ<br />\n月足天音 TII<br />\n豊永阿紀 H<br />\n松本日向 TII<br />\n宮﨑想乃 TII<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=